extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p Welcome to Natours, we're glad to have you 🎉🙏
  p Your account has been created. Your temporary password is: #[strong #{tempPassword}], to log in for the first time use it.
  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}login`, target='_blank') Log in
  p After logging in, please change your password! Do this to prevent anyone else from accessing your account. You can do this in your profile. You can also set your profile picture there so we can get to know each other better!
  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}profile`, target='_blank') Change your password
  p If you need any help with booking your next tour, please don't hesitate to contact me!
  p - Jonas Schmedtmann, CEO